						               													<description>DESCRIPTION:&amp;#10;Have you ever wanted to run your own business?   Whether you want to have a coffee shop, a shoe store, or a fine art establishment..now you can do so at The Mall.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Mall allows 2-5 players to compete for the best retail space and customers to accumulate the most money in the shortest time.  Can you prove how business savvy you are?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GAME OBJECTIVE:&amp;#10;Have the most net worth (cash and properties) once there are not enough customers remaining at The Mall.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GAMEPLAY:&amp;#10;Starting with a small shop at your local mall, players upgrade as quickly as possible and expand into more shops to capture as many customer sales as possible.  Action cards are used to drive customers to each of your shop(s) for maximum revenue.  Marketing cards are used to strategically improve your position or slow down your competition.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As the game progresses, there are less and less customers at the mall, causing the competition to become frenzied as you push for the maximum net worth.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GAME ELEMENTS:&amp;#10;The Mall uses a unique card system to determine movement.  No dice were harmed in the making of this game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
